title: Custom Apartment Search
posting_body: ['I am a licensed professional real estate agent and I am here to help you navigate the housing market.', 'As a Realtor® I subscribe to a strict code of ethics and integrity set forth by the National Association of Realtors.', 'Your best interest is my priority.', 'Please call/text and let me know how I may help you .', '- Tiffany Apartment Locator -', 'show contact info', '<URL>', '*************', 'Apartments', 'Townhomes', 'Luxury Apartments', 'Mid Rise', 'High Rise', 'Penthouse', 'Whenever you lease an apartment and list me as your referral source, the apartment complex pays me a referral fee for bringing them a qualified tenant.', 'I will just need the following from you to get started:', '1.', 'First and Last Name(s)', '2.', 'E-mail(s)', '3.', 'Phone #(s)', '4.', 'Preferred Move-In Date', '5.', 'Desired Location', '6.', 'Price Range', '7.', 'Credit Score Range - best approval odds at 600 or better', 'I am Licensed with the STATE OF TEXAS.', 'My experience includes investors, developers, property management, apartment locating, and residential real estate.', 'Thank you for choosing Bird Nest Team @ Core One Real Estate.', 'I look forward to working with you!', 'Houston | Austin | Galveston | Dallas | San Antonio', 'This is an advertisement for an apartment locating service.', 'Not a specific apartment community.', 'Note- Pricing & Availability Subject', 'To Change', 'If relocating you will need an offer letter.', 'Must have proof of gross income for 3X the rent']
